@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Analyze API" as API
participant "AI Service" as AI
database PostgreSQL

User -> Frontend: Chon anh mon an
Frontend -> API: POST /api/analyze
API -> AI: /predict(image)
AI --> API: prediction
API -> PostgreSQL: save scan_history
API --> Frontend: food + suggestions
Frontend -> API: POST /api/analyze/:scanId/confirm
API -> PostgreSQL: update confirmed + create meal
API --> Frontend: success
@enduml
